---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/989798955176280064
  Locus:
    Date: 27 April 2018
---
There are always problems to face, but it makes a difference if our minds
are calm. On the surface we may get upset, but it makes a difference if
we are able to stay calm in the depths of our minds.
